snippet.title: Hulu
snippet.description:
TONS OF SHOWS AND MOVIES 
Exclusive stuff like every season of It's Always Sunny in Philadelphia and The Golden Girls. Fan faves like Bob’s Burgers and Modern Family. And new hits like Cruel Summer and Big Sky. Oh, plus a huge library of hit movies.
 
ORIGINALS YOU CAN'T STOP WATCHING
Like The Handmaid’s Tale, obviously. But don’t forget about the genre-bending dramedy The Great, the cringe comedy Pen15, the screen adaptation of Shrill, Hulu Original documentaries, and more.
 
LIVE TV FOR SPORTS AND NEWS 
Get all the action on the field, in the rink, and in the newsroom with over 75 live channels at your fingertips. Stream your favorite teams at home or on-the-go.
 
NO CABLE REQUIRED 
Subscriptions start at $5.99/month for Hulu’s entire streaming library, with plenty of options to craft the perfect plan for you. No cable box needed, and you can cancel anytime.
